Tap-to-Pay Fare → Payment Authentication & Security
Every fare transaction must include authentication and security checks. This is mandatory for every payment.
Tap-to-Pay Fare → Payment Confirmation Notification
Each transaction must send a confirmation to the passenger and conductor.
View Transaction History → Tap-to-Pay Fare
Transaction history always depends on completed tap-to-pay transactions being logged.
Generate Reports → System Monitoring
Reports are generated using data collected from system monitoring; this is always required.
